Package qchem Description

Provides the interface with electronic structure programs.
This package contains three functions:
  1. Read input parameters and generate the input file
  2. Provide execution command
  3. Read output file and export to Molecule
The current version supports GAUSSIAN.
Since:
Sindo 3.0
Version:
1.0
Author:
Kiyoshi Yagi
